Package: RBiblioSynth
Type: Package
Title: Bibliometric Analysis and Systematic Review Report Automation
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-03-25
Authors@R: person("Mayorga", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "maintainer@example.com")
Description: A modular framework for automating bibliometric analysis and
    systematic review reporting. Provides modules for main information
    extraction (M1), annual production regression analysis (M2), author
    analysis (M3), and country-level analysis (M4), with support for
    Scopus and OpenAlex data sources.
